            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In domini salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_magnificus #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3010">Secundus Richardus</persName> divina ordinante
                        clementia Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, ob salutem anime sue
                        suorumque parentum hoc donum clementer ac benigne factum est. Nos secundus
                        Richardus divina ordinante clementia Capuanorum princeps, notum fieri
                        volumus omnibus fidelibus nostris, quoniam ob salutem et remedium animarum
                        quondam <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs> predecessorum nostrorum <persName
                            key="#Princeps #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3001">Richardi</persName>
                        silicet <rs key="#grandparentOf">avi</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3002">Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs>, nec non et omnium <rs key="#familyOf"
                            >parentum</rs> nostrorum, <rs key="#Mother_churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3053">beati
                            Pauli</orgName>, que est mater in <rs key="#Cities">urbe</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Dioecesis" ref="#places/4000">Aversana</placeName>,
                        honorare et exaltare cupientes, <rs key="#Intercessory">per interventum
                        </rs>quoque domni <persName key="#Intercessory #Bishops #Personal_rank"
                            ref="#people/3056">Iohannis</persName> eiusdem ecclesie <rs
                            key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>, et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness #Count #childOf" ref="#people/2422"
                            >Robberti</persName>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/4236">Ranulfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>, et nostrorum dilectorum subscriptorum baronum
                            <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/4251">Hugonis
                            videlicet de Molinis</persName>, <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3076">Willelmi de Pirolo</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/3020">Robberti de
                            Medania</persName>, <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness"
                            ref="#people/5016">Thome de Venabile</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/3080">Raynaldi
                            Lupi[ni]</persName>, <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness"
                            ref="#people/5017">Raynaldi de Matalone</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/4253">Ranulfi filii
                            Guale</persName>, <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness"
                            ref="#people/4242">Radulfi de Mucegros</persName>, predicte ecclesie
                        Sancti Pauli apostoli, per hoc principale scriptum in perpetuum damus et
                        tradendo confirmamus, <rs key="#Churches">ecc[lesiam] </rs><orgName
                            key="#Houses #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3802">Sancti Petri Alibissidi</orgName>, sitam
                        in <rs key="#City_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/4014 #places/4717"><geogName
                                key="#City_territory" ref="#estates/3035"
                            >Nucerie</geogName></placeName>, que est in manu nostra, cum <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">villanis</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >presis</rs>, <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>, fabricis et infrabicis, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris cultis et incultis</rs>, arbustis et
                        universis pertinentiis suis, ad possessionem ac potestatem atque
                        dominationem prefate ecclesie Beati Pauli apostoli et memorati domni
                        Iohannis, venerabilis episcopi, cunct[orumque] successorum eius, remota omni
                        inquietudine, contrarietate atque molestia omnium principum successorum
                        nostrorum vel vice principum, comitum vel vice comitum, [iudicum],
                        sculdahorum et castaldeorum, alior[umque omnium morta]lium personarum. Quod
                        si quis huius nostre donationis et traditionis pagine contemptor aut
                        [violator] esse presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">quingentas libras auri
                            purissimi</rs> persolvat, medietatem nostro sac[ro palatio et]
                        medietatem predicte ecclesie Sancti Pauli apostoli Aversane<rs
                            key="#Dioecesis"> s[edis]</rs> et pre[dicto] domno Iohanni venerabili
                        episcopo eiusque successoribus. Solutaque pena librarum, hec nostra donatio,
                        firma, munita atque inconvulsa maneat in perpetuum. Et ut hoc firmius
                        credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur, manu propria subscripsimus et
                        nostri sigilli impressione iussimus insigniri. SIGNUM DOMNI (M) SECUNDI
                        RICHARDI <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">GLORIOSISSIMI</rs> AC <rs
                            key="#Vir_magnificus">MAGNIFICI</rs> PRINCIPIS. + EGO ROBBERTUS <rs
                            key="#Count">COMES</rs>. Ex iussione prephate serenissime potestatis,
                        scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3012"
                            >QUIRIACUS</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">PALATINUS IUDEX</rs>, in anno dominice incarnationis M.
                        nonagesimo quinto, et sextodecimo anno principatus ipsius domni secundi
                        Richardi, gloriosi principis. DATUM <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/4014 #places/4717">NUCERIAE</placeName>, mense octubrio,
                        per indictionem quartam. + Ego Hugo de Molinis. + Ego Raynaldus Lupinus. +
                        Ego Willelmus de Pirolo. + Ego Raynaldus de Matalone. + Ego Robbertus de
                        Medania. + Ego Ranulfus filius Guale. + Ego Thoma de Venabile. + Ego
                        Radulfus de Mucegros. </ab>
